        {
            "title": "大埔吐露港五車相撞  三人受傷",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"貨車上男子被困。網上圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fdf6c1220888db9c70cbe25fe64b3bcd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050812092748555.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">貨車上男子被困。網上圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（8日）晨11時許，大埔吐露港出九龍方向近大埔滘對開發生五車串燒車禍，涉及三部私家車及兩部貨車，其中一部貨車損毀嚴重，乘客位男子被困車內，地上滿佈碎片，事件中共三人受傷。受事故影響，現場多條線封閉，交通嚴重擠塞。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4236436/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"吐露港公路發生五車串燒意外。網上圖片 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0743d1ea9f083d2e7c76d9a693a6f4e3/2025-05/02_3.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        吐露港公路發生五車串燒意外。網上圖片 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4236437/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"吐露港公路發生五車串燒意外。網上圖片 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3413fcf90cd5a605735405dc04806e7c/2025-05/03_2_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\